commit.message: State Python versions support in CHANGELOG better
Make autocurry() and friends support kw-only and pos-only arguments
Fix `@decorator` and its tests in Python 3.7 and earlier
Stop using pos-only args to be compatible with Python 3.7 and earlier

Improve arg introspection via `call._whatever_`

- support kw-only and pos-only args
- support varargs and kwargs
- deal with special cases like pos-only not shadowing an item in kwargs
with the same name

Switch to Python 3 only syntax in a couple of places

Like kwonly and posonly args.
Get rid of pre Python 3.4 backport

Drop namespace helper class

This one is a noop in Python 3 and since Python 2 is dropped it serves
no purpose.
